                "TRN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " 200-m flight path. The main effort",
                "was devoted to cross section measurements near the 2.35",
                "MeV minimum. The transmission for thin sample was",
                "measured by alternating BeO sample with a matching Be",
                "sample. A thick liquid oxygen scatterer was used to",
                "obtain good statistics and small systematic",
                "uncertainties near the 2.35 MeV resonance."
              ]
            }
          ],
